{"tid":810412,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個見過朋友最狗公嘅時候","createTime":"2018-09-08T03:18:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T03:37:23.000Z","uid":207272,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f77c83a0e2f4f3ae7baecc167d68b942955a7410","tid":810412,"uid":207272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T03:18:28.000Z","msg":"我有一個朋友係學校成日都痴埋啲女仔到玩。以前佢有女哦時都照樣同其他女仔玩，又去搞下其他女仔頭髮，拉走人地個髮髻等。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢自己覺得自己冇問題，但佢係圖書館見到自己條女同其他仔咁玩，又覺得自己頭上一片綠。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 然後就分左手。<br />\n畢業旅行，佢又跟埋班女仔去，佢仲要呃個朋友去同裹面其中一個表白，咁明顯個朋友衰左<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重點黎，過左一個月佢同哦個女仔一齊左，屌你，哦個女仔仲要係大波又算唔差，上體育堂時望住個跑步<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解會比個狗公食左，公平咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0093bfc62d3d4d3dcfdc74311a1db966fb800395","tid":810412,"uid":128120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T03:19:34.000Z","msg":"條女受又唔可以怪啲狗公喎"},{"pid":"03bf9d51b4d3a3a6f0e9a8c7161456a8d9a1750d","tid":810412,"uid":177089,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T03:19:40.000Z","msg":"識唔識中文"},{"pid":"70aafce4a76b7077ee314cc7c10bd3bd166a36d0","tid":810412,"uid":33789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T03:21:25.000Z","msg":"哦哦哦哦哦"},{"pid":"040a4274044b99f2647eaf1608ca9b8dd6c49b48","tid":810412,"uid":84525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T03:23:32.000Z","msg":"哦你老母"},{"pid":"db3e6ab5389a19e648488d853d1e473062187651","tid":810412,"uid":6111,"like":2,"dislike":0